## 19. Safety & Guidelines

### WBGT Risk Levels

* 80–85°F: Low
* 85–88°F: Moderate
* 88–90°F: High
* > 90°F: Extreme

### Air Quality Index

* Good → Hazardous scale
* Sensitive groups:

  * Children
  * Elderly
  * People with asthma

